com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.server
Interface ServerPackage

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.ENamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
ServerPackageImpl
public interface ServerPackage
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage

The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
The core model for SOA Deploy. A Topology contains Units. Units contain s, s, and s. Extension domains are encouraged to extend Unit and Capability but not Topology, Requirement, or UnitLink. An object that can be part of a deployable module. See FileArtifact.

See Also:
ServerFactory
